{
  "message": "test(fuzz): extend fuzz_semantic_eq corpus with 18 new adversarial seeds\n\nAdd seeds covering same-dtype, cross-dtype, and null/missing semantics:\n- Same dtype: int_same, float_same, bool_same, utf8_same\n- Different values: int_diff, float_diff, bool_diff\n- Null kinds: null_null, null_nan, null_nat, nan_nat\n- NaN cases: float_nan, float_nan_vs_null\n- Cross-dtype: int_vs_float, int_vs_bool, float_vs_bool\n- Edge values: int_zero, float_zero\n\nAdds replay test fuzz_semantic_eq_bytes_replays_committed_corpus_seeds\nthat validates all 19 seeds (18 new + 1 existing seed-empty.bin).\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
